cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

This paper is about adversarial attacks on deep neural networks for image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes new attack methods, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which could also suggest cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible category.
